{"data":[{"date":"07:41 20/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6): \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2062018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018: Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e0 th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng mang t\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: Bay cao tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 vua Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang trong tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i tr\u1ecb v\u00ec c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng ng\u1edd v\u1ef1c hay c\u1ea3 ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o, tr\u00f9 \u1ebbo. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mu\u00f4n v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1nh gi\u1ec1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh l\u00ec l\u1ee3m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc 19h ng\u00e0y 206 b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc 19h ng\u00e0y 206 b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc-19h-ngay-206-bang-B-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-463-188575.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 3-3 derby b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia</span> l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i hai l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec7t ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00fa hat-trick si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng knock-out cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, Iran v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u1ed1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Maroc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo!</span><br>\r\nBa b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng Sochi, Cristiano Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Iran kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u00eam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sau ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maroc: T\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t S\u01b0 T\u1eed<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00fang, v\u1edbi c\u00e1nh chim \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0n Ronaldo l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi \u1edf ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga (8 b\u00e0n/2 tr\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018). Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh ra, \u201cBrazil Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\u201d th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 thi tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e0n l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Maroc, m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u201cl\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i\u201d \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb B\u1eafc Phi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc-(19h00-ngay-206)-An-tu-dau-tien-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 70% th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ph\u00fat 90+5 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean, Maroc kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh hai v\u00e9 v\u00f2ng knock-out, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t h\u1ecd l\u00e0 hai ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai T\u00e2y \u2013 B\u1ed3. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ed5 t\u00edch s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Maroc c\u0169ng \u00fd th\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1i d\u1ed9t d\u00e2ng cao ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 l\u1ed9 ra ph\u00eda sau nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2ng cho Ronaldo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ri\u00eang c\u0169ng v\u1eady, cho n\u00ean HLV Herve Renand s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u201ch\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Iran, Maroc ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi qu\u00e1 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a n\u01a1i th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Medhi Benatia, ng\u00f4i sao t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u00f3 th\u1eeba.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bo Dao Nha vs Maroc\" title=\"Preview B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u01b0 T\u1eed Atlas \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft v\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho h\u1ecd trong m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t sinh t\u1eed. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u00ec 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i canh b\u1ea1c \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n gi\u1eef v\u1eefng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady th\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t t\u00f2ng t\u00e2m, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Maroc ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 g\u00e2y ra b\u1edfi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng mang t\u00ean Ronaldo. T\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng Euro s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (4-4-2):\u00a0<o:p></o:p>1. Patricio;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>21. Soares \u2013 3. Pepe \u2013 6. Fonte \u2013 5. Guerreiro;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>11. Silva \u2013 8. Moutinho \u2013 14. Carvalho \u2013 4. Fernandes;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>7. Ronaldo \u2013 17. Guedes<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Maroc (4-2-3-1):\u00a0<o:p></o:p>12. Mohamedi;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>2. Hakimi \u2013 5. Benatia \u2013 6. Saiss \u2013 3. Mendyl;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>14. Boussoufa \u2013 8. Ahmadi;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>7. Ziyech \u2013 10. Belhanda \u2013 18. Harit;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>9. Kaabi<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc: 3-1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc-(19h00-ngay-206)-An-tu-dau-tien-hinh-anh-4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t La Roja h\u1ed7n mang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK World Cup 2018 ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Seleccao \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"371","checkdouble":"188986"},{"date":"07:12 20/06","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/goc-nhin-salah-tro-lai-nhung-sao-khong-the-loi-hai-nhu-o-liverpool.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, NHM \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf sau khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Salah l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Salah ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea3 vai kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi &lsquo;\u0111\u00f4 v\u1eadt&rsquo; Sergio Ramos trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft UEFA Champions League 2017/18 di\u1ec5n ra h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-tran-dau-bang-a-world-cup-2018-421-188574.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, d\u00f9 trong th\u00e2m t\u00e2m anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n m\u1ecdi toan t\u00ednh c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp, m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Salah n\u00f3 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho th\u1eddi gian anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0169ng v\u1eaby \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u1edf n\u00ean ng\u1eafn l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u1ee9u tinh c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y,&nbsp;HLV H\u00e9ctor C\u00faper \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Salah t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u1edbn h\u01a1n cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi, m\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi n\u1ed7i t\u1ec7. Hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i thay phi\u00ean nhau ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-ai-cap-421-188956.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m. Pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 pha x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng minh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi xoay ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Salah. Tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, do m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean Salah \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 &lsquo;sung&rsquo;. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 4 c\u00fa s\u00fat, 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn. Salah ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t do ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o ra. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i pressing \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn &lsquo;Messi Ai C\u1eadp&rsquo; m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t trong su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp, v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn The Pharaohs ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>V\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Liverpool <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Salah t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh trong l\u00e0ng t\u00fac c\u1ea7u gi\u00e1o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi Salah s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3ng vai &lsquo;Ch\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf&rsquo; gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Goc-nhin-Salah-tro-lai-nhung-sao-khong-the-loi-hai-nhu-tai-Liverpool-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u01a1 Salah s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o c\u00f9ng Liverpool tuy nhi\u00ean Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0a The Kop v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League danh gi\u00e1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngang ng\u1eeda. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Salah kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia. V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 Salah \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018-461-188983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018-461-188983.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u00e2\u0301t ba\u0323i 1-3 khi\u00ea\u0301n \u0110T Ai C\u00e2\u0323p g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 bi\u0323 loa\u0323i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018, trong khi \u0111o\u0301 \u0111\u00f4\u0323i chu\u0309 nha\u0300 Nga g\u00e2\u0300n nh\u01b0 \u0111a\u0303 gia\u0300nh t\u00e2\u0301m ve\u0301 va\u0300o vo\u0300ng 1/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep-465-188982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep-465-188982.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup-469-188985.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup-469-188985.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ai C\u1eadp, Nga l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu \u1edf World Cup</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u0103ng hoa sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"370","checkdouble":"188989"},{"date":"07:28 20/06","title":"Ba Lan thua \u0111au Senegal b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ba-lan-thua-dau-senegal-boi-su-yeu-kem-cua-trong-tai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 cho Senegal \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb pha c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng \"b\u1ea5t th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh\" c\u1ee7a Niang t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ba Lan, l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">2 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng H \u0111\u1ec1u mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng Colombia, ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Senegal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Ban-thang-cua-Niang-tran-Ba-Lan-vs-Senegal-khong-hop-le-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho ph\u00e9p Niang v\u00e0o s\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2. \u1ea2nh: Daily Mail.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\r\nS\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111en, Senegal g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho &ldquo;\u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo;. Trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng n\u1eb1m ch\u1eafc trong tay Senegal khi Niang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u00e0o ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 60. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Szczesny \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n non c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Song Niang, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Serie A, b\u1ea5t th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00f3a ra, sau khi \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbaye Niang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho ph\u00e9p ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ba Lan, anh &quot;l\u00e9n l\u00fat&quot; di chuy\u1ec3n ra sau l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u00e0 theo lu\u1eadt ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Niang nhanh chong ap vao cuop bong tu hang thu cua Ba Lan. Anh: AP.\" title=\"Niang nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ba Lan. \u1ea2nh: AP.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/aq.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Niang nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ba Lan. \u1ea2nh: AP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5 ra m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tranh c\u00e3i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n \u00fd ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t, t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai s\u00f3t c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nguy hi\u1ec3m. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Fox n\u00f3i: &quot;Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n th\u00ec m\u1edbi cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n&quot;. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n M\u1ef9, Alexi Lalas \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang gi\u00fap Senegal v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ba Lan c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1-2 \u1edf ph\u00fat 86, tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbt v\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.<br />\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-tang-boc-man-ra-quan-hoan-hao-cua-senegal-469-188981.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Senegal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-ba-lan-12-senegal-421-188976.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ba Lan, HLV \u0110T Senegal t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ch\u00e2u Phi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-senegal-danh-bai-ba-lan-465-188973.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Senegal khi\u1ebfn Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"369","checkdouble":"188991"},{"date":"07:32 20/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (20/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2062018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f