);\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"368","checkdouble":"188992"},{"date":"08:37 20/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha (1h ng\u00e0y 21/6): B\u1edfi La Roja v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u2026","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-216-boi-la-roja-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 HLV m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>TBN \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u0110N</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n qua l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u00ean \u1ea3 v\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ecd sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho TBN trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t Nga b\u1edfi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong v\u00f2ng 2 n\u0103m b\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c b\u1ecb thay b\u1eb1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch&hellip; 2 ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fernando Hierro tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f4n ngoan. Thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1eadp \u0111i x\u00e2y l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 y nguy\u00ean nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng 2 n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1h ng\u00e0y 216 Tin v\u00e0o La Roja h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1h ng\u00e0y 216 Tin v\u00e0o La Roja h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Iran-vs-Tay-Ban-Nha-1h-ngay-216-Tin-vao-La-Roja-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">TBN kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 suy y\u1ebfu b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua tranh c\u00e3i ngay nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1edfi sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd d\u1eabn 3-2 nh\u1edb c\u00fa s\u00fat xa ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Nacho. 2 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, La Roja \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1edfi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo giup BDN co tran hoa 3-3 truoc TBN\" title=\"Ronaldo gi\u00fap B\u0110N c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/lap-hattrick-ronaldo-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi-het-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">La Roja ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a b\u1edfi c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Diego Costa \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Atletico Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f3a \u0111i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh tr\u00ean \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn, T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, n\u01a1i Costa th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00f2n b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 t\u1edbi sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea7m xa c\u1ee7a Nacho, n\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf TBN \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p khi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng ng\u1eafn m\u1ea5t t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng b\u1edfi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u0110N.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u r\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1m sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui. V\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Iran vs Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Preview Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Iran-vs-TBN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1h ng\u00e0y 21/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>La Roja v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ecf qua c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao, ch\u1ec9 sau c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 Brazil, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1ea1i d\u00e0nh cho La Roja khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 ch\u00fat b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Man United c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, khi\u1ebfn TBN b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, De Gea th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin khi ra qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fernando Hierro noi ve tran BDN vs TBN\" title=\"Fernando Hierro n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N vs TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/hlv-hierro-khong-muon-dt-tay-ban-nha-di-vao-vet-xe-do-cua-nguoi-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV&nbsp;Hierro v\u1eabn gi\u00fap TBN c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ca-tay-ban-nha-dung-ve-de-gea-sau-dem-gap-bo-tham-hoa-421-188682.html\" target=\"_blank\">c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 De Gea sau \u0111\u00eam th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi B\u0110N</span>. H\u1ebft HLV Hierro, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ramos \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Costa \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 27 tu\u1ed5i. Tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a TBN l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng khen v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p De Gea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iran l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i TBN n\u00f3i chung ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a La Roja v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Iran co chien thang thu hai tai World Cup\" title=\"\u0110T Iran c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Tu-tran-Maroc-0-1-DT-Iran-nghi-ve-bong-da-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Iran kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nIran \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma-r\u1ed1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Aziz Bouhaddouz. Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Iran b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tho\u00e1t thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Ma-r\u1ed1c t\u1ecf ra n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 phung ph\u00ed c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c &ldquo;Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed Ba T\u01b0&rdquo;. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 TBN ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nIran (4-1-4-1): </strong>1.Beiranvand - 23.Rezaeian, 4.Cheshmi, 8.Pouraliganji, 3.Safi - 9.Ebrahimi - 18.Jahanbakhsh, 7.Shojaei, 11.Amiri, 10.Ansarifard - 20.Azmoun.<br>\r\n<strong>T\u00e2y Ban Nha (4-3-3): </strong>1.De Gea - 4.Nacho, 3.Pique, 15.Ramos, 18.Alba - 8.Koke, 5.Busquets, 6.Iniesta - 22.Isco, 19.Costa, 21.Silva.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: TBN th\u1eafng 3-0<br>\r\n</strong><strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T TBN tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-dt-tay-ban-nha-bao-tin-mung-ve-chan-thuong-cua-dani-carvajal-421-188977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/19/hlv-dt-tay-ban-nha-bao-tin-mung-ve-chan-thuong-cua-dani-carvajal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-dt-tay-ban-nha-bao-tin-mung-ve-chan-thuong-cua-dani-carvajal-421-188977.html\">HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Iran, HLV Hierro \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Dani Carvajal.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/casillas-len-tieng-bao-ve-de-gea-sau-man-ra-quan-kem-duyen-421-188965.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/casillas-len-tieng-bao-ve-de-gea-sau-man-ra-quan-kem-duyen.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/casillas-len-tieng-bao-ve-de-gea-sau-man-ra-quan-kem-duyen-421-188965.html\">Casillas l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 De Gea sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n k\u00e9m duy\u00ean</span><br>\r\n<span>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha Iker Casillas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a &lsquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n em&rsquo; David De Gea t\u1ea1i VCK World...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"367","checkdouble":"188993"},{"date":"08:53 20/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia (22h00 ng\u00e0y 20/06): Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-22h00-ngay-2006-thien-duong-va-dia-nguc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Suarez v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua n\u1eefa Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n trong tay m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e9 s\u1edbm cho Uruguay?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Gimenez v\u00e0 Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Edison Cavani &ndash; Luis Suarez.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Saudi-Arabia-Thien-duong-va-dia-nguc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/ai-cap-vs-uruguay-bang-a-463-188549.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ai C\u1eadp</span>. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 59% v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 (16 so v\u1edbi 8). C\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuis Suarez c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi, Edison Cavani c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mohamed El-Shenawy.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Ph\u00fat 89, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c trung v\u1ec7 Jose Gimenez \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia\" title=\"Preview Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Uruguay-vs-Saudi-Arabia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Cavani hay Suarez vi\u1ec7c Uruguay ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, song \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Uruguay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Oscar Tabarez \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga gi\u00e0nh 2 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 Uzbekistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0. Luis Suarez ghi 1 trong 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, Suarez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u1eaft NHM \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ee7a Suarez c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Oscar Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia (22h00 ng\u00e0y 2006) Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia (22h00 ng\u00e0y 2006) Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Saudi-Arabia-(22h00-ngay-2006)-Thien-duong-va-dia-nguc-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Saudi Arabia thua Nga 0-5 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng A</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Saudi Arabia ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc khi ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1&nbsp;t\u1ec7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 thua khi tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 h\u1ed3n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec l\u00e0m x\u1ea5u \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga khi\u1ebfn Saudi Arabia n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tham d\u1ef1 World Cup. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 VCK World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o, v\u1edbi h\u00f2a 2, thua 7.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, Saudi Arabia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua n\u1eefa khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Uruguay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin gop dau giay vao 3/5 ban thang cua Nga truoc Saudi Arabia\" title=\"Golovin g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 3/5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/may-bay-cho-tuyen-saudi-arabia-phut-lua-tren-troi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thua Uruguay, Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ghi b\u00e0n, song ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao c\u1ee7a Nga, Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n thua. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ee7a Uruguay nh\u01b0 Suarez hay Cavani, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Al-Mayouf gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n trong tay m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Uruguay-vs-Saudi-Arabia-(4-3-1-2-vs-4-1-4-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 3-0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"366","checkdouble":"188998"},{"date":"01:42 20/06","title":"HLV \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/19/hlv-dt-tay-ban-nha-bao-tin-mung-ve-chan-thuong-cua-dani-carvajal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Iran, HLV Hierro \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Dani Carvajal.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hierro</span>&nbsp;b\u00e1o tin Dani Carvajal b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 gi\u1eefa Real Madrid v\u00e0 Liverpool, Dani Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng \u1edf g\u00e2n khoeo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 anh c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng g\u00f3t cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n.&nbsp;Ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Carvajal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi VCK World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro b\u00e1o tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hierro b\u00e1o tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/HLV-Hierro-bao-tin-mung-ve-chan-thuong-cua-Dani-Carvajal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Dani Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian qua, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c kh\u00e1 nhanh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a La Roja.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Iran, HLV Hierro b\u00e1o tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Carvajal kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i trong su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n qua. Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00e1c b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ch\u1ec9 \u00edt ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup kh\u1edfi tranh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n qu\u00ean B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Iran. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 s\u1ed1ng m\u00e3i v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Carlos Queiroz, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u1ecfi. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Iran 7 n\u0103m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd. Iran l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh trong c\u1ea3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1eabn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-khong-muon-dt-tay-ban-nha-di-vao-vet-xe-do-cua-nguoi-duc-421-188972.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-hierro-khong-muon-dt-tay-ban-nha-di-vao-vet-xe-do-cua-nguoi-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-khong-muon-dt-tay-ban-nha-di-vao-vet-xe-do-cua-nguoi-duc-421-188972.html\">HLV Hierro kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, HLV Fernando Hierro c\u1ee7a \u0110T TBN \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf k\u1ef3 World...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-man-ra-quan-that-vong-cua-cac-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188916.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/thay-gi-sau-man-ra-quan-that-vong-cua-cac-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-man-ra-quan-that-vong-cua-cac-ung-vien-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188916.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u01afCV n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c &lsquo;\u00f4ng l\u1edbn&rsquo; l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"365","checkdouble":"188977"},{"date":"01:55 20/06","title":"HLV Adam Nawalka n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hlv-adam-nawalka-chia-se-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-ba-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Adam Nawalka kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Ba Lan l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua Senegal v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-2. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn DDT Ba La ph\u01a1i \u00e1o trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n l\u00e0 do nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, khi c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng thi\u1ebfu t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Adam Nawalka chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Adam Nawalka chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/hlv-adam-nawalka-chia-se-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-ba-lan.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Adam Nawalka chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7t \u0110T Ba Lan v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng HLV Adam Nawalka kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng: &quot;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia, \u0110T Ba Lan s\u1ebd \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i tin ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd duy tr\u00ec th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00f3i g\u00ec<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a HLV Nawalka, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Arkadiusz Milik kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ba Lan trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Senegal \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft Senegal ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t hay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. Gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ba Lan v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Colombia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 25/6) v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (21h00 ng\u00e0y 28/6).<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-ba-lan-12-senegal-421-188976.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ba Lan, HLV \u0110T Senegal t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ch\u00e2u Phi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-ba-lan-12-senegal-bang-h-world-cup-2018-461-188974.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-senegal-danh-bai-ba-lan-465-188973.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Senegal khi\u1ebfn Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal-463-188940.html\">Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal (KT): S\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga b\u1eafn r\u1ee5ng \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-ba-lan-vs-senegal-22h-ngay-196-dai-phao-so-tai-462-188897.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ba Lan vs Senegal (22h ng\u00e0y 19/6): \u0110\u1ea1i ph\u00e1o so t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"364","checkdouble":"188978"},{"date":"02:09 20/06","title":"HLV \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-dt-bo-dao-nha-phu-nhan-su-phu-thuoc-vao-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nh\u1ecf nhoi. \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Saudi Arabia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f9 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/salah-20.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t mong manh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, Nga v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. Trong khi Uruguay v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 ba \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng Saudi Arabia c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1. Ngo\u00e0i ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0110T Nga ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ba \u0111\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp, Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Uruguay c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi c\u00f3 ba \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m theo quy ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a FIFA, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Uruguay v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp r\u1ea5t mong manh b\u1edfi Saudi Arabia b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Uruguay - \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady khi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a l\u0103n, ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-ai-cap-463-188953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/ket-qua-nga-vs-ai-cap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-ai-cap-463-188953.html\">Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp (KT): Salah ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n, The Pharaohs v\u1eabn ch\u1ebft th\u1ea3m d\u01b0\u1edbi tay b\u1ea7y G\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 01h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"363","checkdouble":"188979"},{"date":"02:49 20/06","title":"CLB Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai trong h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Arsenal m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 hai trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c Bernd Leno \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen.</h2><h2>CLB Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, trang ch\u1ee7 Arsenal.com c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Bernd Leno. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ra s\u00e2n h\u01a1n 230 l\u1ea7n cho Bayer Leverkusen k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y n\u0103m 2011, Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Champions League trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Bayer Leverkusen v\u00e0 Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 2011. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 Leno m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i 193 ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Arsenal thong bao chieu mo thanh cong thu thanh Bernd Leno\" title=\"CLB Arsenal th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><i>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG, Bernd Leno \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Joachim Low tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Die Mannschaft. T\u1ea1i Confederations Cup 2017, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0y, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eadt vinh h\u1ea1nh khi Bernd Leno gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Leverkusen \u1edf Bundesliga su\u1ed1t 7 n\u0103m qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Bernd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Arsenal v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng anh \u1ea5y trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal </span>\u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, Petr Cech nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi m\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh CH S\u00e9c n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 36 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n David Luiz cho Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nArsenal mua David Luiz nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Chelsea v\u1eeba t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/premier-league-chinh-thuc-cong-bo-lich-thi-dau-mua-giai-201819-172-188479.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/premier-league-chinh-thuc-cong-bo-lich-thi-dau-mua-giai-201819.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/premier-league-chinh-thuc-cong-bo-lich-thi-dau-mua-giai-201819-172-188479.html\">Premier League ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</span><br>\r\nBan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Premier League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Arsenal c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 vui c\u01b0\u1eddi cho n\u1ed5i khi ph\u1ea3i m\u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"362","checkdouble":"188980"},{"date":"03:03 20/06","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Senegal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/huyen-thoai-tang-boc-man-ra-quan-hoan-hao-cua-senegal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i El Hadji Diouf c\u1ee7a Senegal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ba Lan v\u1eeba qua.</h2><h2>Senegal th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Ba Lan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Thiago Cionek v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a M\u2019Baye Niang trong hi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal-463-188940.html\" target=\"_blank\">Senegal gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</span>. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Krychowiak l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ba Lan gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb tay \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEl Hadji Diouf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Aliou Cisse \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup sau 16 n\u0103m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Senegal c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, Diouf t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Senegal c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, Diouf t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/huyen-thoai-tang-boc-man-ra-quan-hoan-hao-cua-senegal.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Senegal c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, Diouf \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi k\u00eanh Omnisport v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Senegal.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Senegal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd ch\u1edd to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, Senegal s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Colombia. V\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt n\u00e0y, \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga\u201d s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1eeba qua. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o\u1ea1t m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb b\u1ea3ng H.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSenegal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 \u0111o\u00e1n bi\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu Colombia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb s\u1edbm \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. V\u1eady n\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Senegal thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tay h\u1ecd.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn Senegal vs Ba Lan:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ba Lan, HLV \u0110T Senegal t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ch\u00e2u Phi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-ba-lan-12-senegal-bang-h-world-cup-2018-461-188974.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"361","checkdouble":"188981"},{"date":"03:07 20/06","title":"Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nh\u1ecf nhoi. \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Saudi Arabia ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f9 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/salah-20.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t mong manh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, Nga v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. Trong khi Uruguay v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 ba \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng Saudi Arabia c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1. Ngo\u00e0i ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0110T Nga ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ba \u0111\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp, Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Uruguay c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi c\u00f3 ba \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m theo quy ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a FIFA, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Uruguay v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp r\u1ea5t mong manh b\u1edfi Saudi Arabia b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Uruguay - \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady khi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a l\u0103n, ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-ai-cap-463-188953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/ket-qua-nga-vs-ai-cap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-ai-cap-463-188953.html\">Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp (KT): Salah ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n, The Pharaohs v\u1eabn ch\u1ebft th\u1ea3m d\u01b0\u1edbi tay b\u1ea7y G\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 01h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"360","checkdouble":"188982"},{"date":"03:14 20/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00e2\u0301t ba\u0323i 1-3 khi\u00ea\u0301n \u0110T Ai C\u00e2\u0323p g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 bi\u0323 loa\u0323i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018, trong khi \u0111o\u0301 \u0111\u00f4\u0323i chu\u0309 nha\u0300 Nga g\u00e2\u0300n nh\u01b0 \u0111a\u0303 gia\u0300nh t\u00e2\u0301m ve\u0301 va\u0300o vo\u0300ng 1/8.</h2>Link xem: <span href=\"http://worldcup.vtv.vn/tin-tuc-app-the-thao/xem-truc-tiep-fifa-world-cup-2018-dt-nga-dt-ai-cap-20180620001812569.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://worldcup.vtv.vn/tin-tuc-app-the-thao/xem-truc-tiep-fifa-world-cup-2018-dt-nga-dt-ai-cap-20180620001812569.htm</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV<br />\r\n\u0110\u00f4\u0323i hi\u0300nh thi \u0111\u00e2\u0301u<br />\r\nNga: Akinfeev, Fernandes, Kutepov, Ignashevich, Zhirkov, Gazinskiy, Zobnin, Samedov, Golovin, Cheryshev, Dzyuba<br />\r\nAi C\u00e2\u0323p: El Shenawy; Abdelshafy, Hegazy, Gabr, Fathy; Hamed, Elneny; Trezeguet, Elsaid, Salah; Mohsen<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"359","checkdouble":"188983"},{"date":"04:00 20/06","title":"\"T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3\" Sanchez n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Colombia thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/toi-do-sanchez-noi-gi-sau-khi-colombia-thua-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Carlos Sanchez kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa n\u00e0o cho t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Colombia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>&ldquo;T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3&rdquo; Sanchez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sao-colombia-suyt-lap-ky-luc-ve-thoi-gian-nhan-the-do-tai-world-cup-421-188963.html\" target=\"_blank\">Carlos Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf</span> ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 khi d\u00f9ng tay ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Shinji Kagawa trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Colombia. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf nhanh th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Carlos Sanchez kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c khi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn tr\u00ean k\u00eanh TV Globo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sanchez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/toi-do-sanchez-noi-gi-sau-khi-colombia-thua-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Carlos Sanchez nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 nh\u01b0 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng. Nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u1ed5n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t knock-out \u1edf World Cup&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<h2>Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7</h2>\r\nSanchez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c anh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Falcao \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Sanchez:<em> &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n:<em> &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng n\u00ean ng\u1eebng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Jose Pekerman l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng Colombia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;\u1ede m\u1eb7t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t t\u1edbi t\u1eeb to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</em><strong><em>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Colombia:</em></strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-colombia-12-nhat-ban-bang-h-world-cup-2018-461-188955.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Colombia:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-jose-pekerman-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-truoc-nhat-ban-421-188958.html\">HLV \u0110T Colombia n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-colombia-12-nhat-ban-421-188960.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia 1-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"358","checkdouble":"188984"},{"date":"04:33 20/06","title":"H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ai C\u1eadp, Nga l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu \u1edf World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u0103ng hoa sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i World Cup.</h2><h2>Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ai C\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nga l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Nga \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-0. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Stanislav Cherchesov c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bang-a-world-cup-2018-gau-hay-pharaon-421-187742.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span> sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ai C\u1eadp, l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu \u1edf World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ai C\u1eadp, l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu \u1edf World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai g\u1eb7p Ai C\u1eadp, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. Ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai, Nga m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Ahmed Fathy. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t an to\u00e0n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 62 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Salah gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp g\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t penalty. Nh\u01b0ng Nga \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef v\u1eefng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<h2>K\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u1ec9 sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u Nga \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e3 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u0103m 1934, Italia c\u0169ng t\u1eebng m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n sau 2 tr\u1eadn. Sau 84 n\u0103m, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga san l\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Stanislav Cherchesov \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n ngang b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Nam Phi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung ch\u00fa \u00fd sang v\u00f2ng knock-out.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep-465-188982.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018-461-188983.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"357","checkdouble":"188985"}]}